      "span_text": "The ongoing international, multicenter, double-blind, parallel-group, 3-year Finding Optimum Regimen for DMD (FOR-DMD) trial (NCT01603407) comparing daily and intermittent regimens of prednisone to daily deflazacort in approximately 300 patients with DMD may further augment the understanding of benefits associated with these 2 steroid treatments and 2 regimens (daily versus intermittent)."
